#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:3
msgid "Postponed Election"
msgstr "Etholiad wedi'i ohirio"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:5
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This election has been postponed due to the death of one of the "
"candidates. A new election will be held within 35 working days of the "
"initial election date (%(initial_poll_date)s)."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r etholiad hwn wedi'i ohirio oherwydd marwolaeth un o'r ymgeiswyr. "
"Bydd etholiad newydd yn cael ei gynnal o fewn 35 diwrnod gwaith o'r "
"dyddiad etholiad cychwynnol (%(initial_poll_date)s)."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:15
#, python-format
msgid ""
"No candidates stood for the available seats, so no election can be held. "
"The election will be rescheduled and held within 35 days of the original "
"polling day (%(initial_poll_date)s)."
msgstr ""
"Canslwyd yr etholiad hwn oherwydd na safodd unrhyw ymgeiswyr ar gyfer y "
"seddau sydd ar gael. Bydd yn cael ei aildrefnu a'i gynnal o fewn 35 "
"diwrnod gwaith o'r diwrnod pleidleisio cychwynnol "
"(%(initial_poll_date)s)."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:24
msgid "Uncontested Election"
msgstr "Etholiad wedi ei herio"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:27
msgid ""
"No election will be held because the number of candidates who stood was "
"equal to the number of available seats. The following candidates will "
"take up this position:"
msgstr ""
"Ni chynhelir etholiad oherwydd bod nifer yr ymgeiswyr a safodd yn hafal i"
" nifer y seddi sydd ar gael. Bydd yr ymgeiswyr canlynol yn cymryd y swydd"
" hon:"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:42
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This election was postponed because the number of candidates who stood "
"was fewer than the number of available seats. The election will be "
"rescheduled and held within 35 days of the original polling day "
"(%(initial_poll_date)s)."
msgstr ""
"Fe ohiriwyd yr etholiad hwn gan fod nifer yr ymgeiswyr a safodd yn llai "
"na nifer y seddau sydd ar gael. Bydd yr etholiad yn cael ei aildrefnu a'i"
" gynnal o fewn 35 diwrnod o'r diwrnod pleidleisio gwreiddiol "
"(%(initial_poll_date)s)."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/feedback_section.html:2
msgid "Feedback"
msgstr "Adborth"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/feedback_section.html:4
msgid ""
"Did you find what you were looking for? If not, <a "
"href=\"/node/24756\">let us know</a>"
msgstr ""
"A wnaethoch chi ddod o hyd i'r hyn roeddech yn chwilio amdano? Os na, <a "
"href=\"/node/24756\">rhowch wybod i ni</a>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/html_meta.html:9
msgid ""
"Enter your postcode to find your electoral services team at your local "
"council. You need to send your postal and proxy vote application forms to"
" them."
msgstr ""
"Nodwch eich cod post i ddod o hyd i wybodaeth am eich tîm gwasanaeth "
"etholiadol yn eich cyngor lleol. Bydd angen i chi anfon eich ceisiadau "
"pleidlais bost neu bleidlais drwy ddirprwy i'ch gwasanaeth etholiadol "
"lleol."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/html_meta.html:13
#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/html_meta.html:19
msgid ""
"Find upcoming elections in your area, your polling station, candidates, "
"and contact details for your local electoral services team"
msgstr ""
"Dewch o hyd i etholiadau sydd ar ddod yn eich ardal, eich gorsaf "
"bleidleisio, ymgeiswyr, a manylion cyswllt eich tîm gwasanaethau "
"etholiadol lleol"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:4
msgid "Get help with electoral registration"
msgstr "Cael cymorth gyda chofrestru etholiadol"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:7
msgid ""
"Send your postal and proxy vote applications to your local electoral "
"registration team. You can also contact them to find out if you’re on the"
" electoral register, and if you already have a postal or proxy vote."
msgstr ""
"Anfonwch eich ceisiadau pleidleisio post a dirprwy i'ch tîm cofrestru "
"etholiadol lleol. Gallwch hefyd gysylltu â hwy i ddarganfod a ydych chi "
"ar y gofrestr etholiadol, ac os oes gennych bleidlais post neu dirprwy "
"eisoes."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:16
msgid "Electoral Office for Northern Ireland"
msgstr "Swyddfa Etholiadol Gogledd Iwerddon"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:18
msgid ""
"For questions about your poll card, polling place, or about returning "
"your postal voting ballot, contact the Electoral Office for Northern "
"Ireland."
msgstr ""
"Am gwestiynau am eich cerdyn pleidleisio, eich man pleidleisio, neu am "
"ddychwelyd eich papur pleidleisio post, cysylltwch â Swyddfa Etholiadol "
"Gogledd Iwerddon."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:26
msgid ""
"<p>For questions about your poll card, polling station, or about "
"returning your postal voting ballot, contact your council.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Am gwestiynau am eich cerdyn pleidleisio, eich gorsaf bleidleisio, neu"
" am ddychwelyd eich papur pleidleisio post, cysylltwch â'ch cyngor.</p>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:33
msgid ""
"<p> Here are contact details for your usual election team. However, for "
"some elections, electoral boundaries mean that your neighbouring election"
" team may be responsible for the constituency you are in. Your usual "
"election team will be able to provide their contact details if this is "
"the case. </p>"
msgstr ""

